				<wikidot:authorName>TL333s</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1304786</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I hope people find this thing as <em>fucking horrifying</em> as I do. I'm only tagging it scp and euclid for starters, so as not to incur the wrath of Aelanna.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilered&nbsp;commentary</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>So one day, the universe got bored. It looked around itself and, feeling pranky, went, &quot;Fuuuuuuuuck&#8230; <em>that guy</em>.&quot; And then it had a laugh for two seconds, got bored, and turned its attention elsewhere. It forgot to hit the off switch.</p> </div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers</a></div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
